text: Shock is a 1946 American thriller movie directed by Alfred L. Werker and starring Vincent Price, Lynn Bari, Frank Latimore, Anabel Shaw, Stephen Dunne, Reed Hadley. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1946 thriller movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred L. Werker
